  "name": "Weapon Proficiency (EitR)",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/feats/exotic-weapon-proficiency.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Choose&nbsp; one&nbsp; weapon&nbsp; group&nbsp; listed&nbsp; under&nbsp; the&nbsp; fighter&rsquo;s&nbsp; Weapon&nbsp; Training&nbsp; class&nbsp; feature.&nbsp; You&nbsp; understand&nbsp; how&nbsp; to&nbsp; use all weapons from that group.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">You&nbsp; make&nbsp; attack&nbsp; rolls&nbsp; with&nbsp; weapons&nbsp; from&nbsp; the selected group normally (without the non-proficient penalty).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Normal</strong></p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">When&nbsp; using&nbsp; a&nbsp; weapon&nbsp; with&nbsp; which&nbsp; you&nbsp; are&nbsp; not proficient, you take a &ndash;4 penalty on attack rolls.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Special</strong></p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">You&nbsp; can&nbsp; gain&nbsp; Weapon&nbsp; Proficiency&nbsp; multiple&nbsp; times.&nbsp; Each&nbsp; time&nbsp; you&nbsp; take&nbsp; the&nbsp; feat,&nbsp; it&nbsp; applies&nbsp; to&nbsp; a&nbsp; new&nbsp; weapon group.</p>",
